title: Unexpected!
author: VD
content_html:
The polls were never meaningful, but they are just straight up fiction now.

Stunning poll reveals Kamala Harris has taken the lead over Trump in unexpected state as momentum swings to VP with three days left.

Sure it has. When literally nothing has happened and nothing has been done. What passes for “democracy” in America is now little more than a scripted fraud. Remember, Kamala couldn’t get more than one percent support in the Democratic primaries.

Pure fiction, no matter what “happens” in what is supposed to pass for an election next week.
